Titolo: Cold Iron (video game)

Anno: 2018

Descrizione: Cold Iron is a 2018 virtual reality first-person shooter video game developed and published by Catch & Release, LLC for HTC Vive, PlayStation VR, and Oculus Rift. The game is presented in a first-person perspective, with a primary focus on fast draw and puzzle solving gameplay. Cold Iron was released on January 30, 2018.